course.subject: FINA
course.name: Communications for Finance Professionals
course.description: This course provides students with tools for communicating in the workplace, in particular, the finance industry, as well as ways to apply those skills. It covers personal branding, online and offline networking, presentation and selling skills. Students will learn how to communicate to win with internal and external clients. They will also learn valuable time management techniques and ways to manage work life in the fast-paced financial sector.
